      <title>英国预算：财政大臣里夫斯重要声明摘要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/uk-budget-highlights-of-chancellor-reeves-key-announcements</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣 Rachel Reeves 宣布了政府在首位女性财政大臣制定的预算中的经济和财政重点。Reeves 在伦敦下议院发表讲话时宣布了 400 亿英镑（518 亿美元）的增税措施，包括增加企业的国家保险工资税和资本利得税。她还提高了基金经理利润（即附带权益）的资本利得税率，并承诺结束为该国最富有的外国人提供税收减免的制度。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/uk-budget-highlights-of-chancellor-reeves-key-announcements</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 16:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管存在危险信号，Polymarket 对华尔街选举“游戏计划”的影响力仍在不断增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/polymarket-s-influence-on-wall-street-s-game-plan-grows-despite-red-flags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管人们普遍怀疑投资者应该在多大程度上相信加密货币预测市场 Polymarket 发出的信号，但华尔街仍密切关注该平台上的押注，该平台显示唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选的可能性很高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/polymarket-s-influence-on-wall-street-s-game-plan-grows-despite-red-flags</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 16:16:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>施纳贝尔称欧洲央行不应仓促进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/ecb-mustn-t-rush-further-interest-rate-cuts-schnabel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔表示，欧洲央行不应急于降低借贷成本，将利率降至所谓中性利率以下来刺激经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/ecb-mustn-t-rush-further-interest-rate-cuts-schnabel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 16:11:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受选举风险影响，美元对冲成本飙升至 2022 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/dollar-hedging-costs-surge-to-most-since-2022-on-election-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员为下周总统大选后市场大幅波动的风险做准备，对冲美元波动的黄金价格飙升至近两年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/dollar-hedging-costs-surge-to-most-since-2022-on-election-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 16:02:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
